The '''Flatlands''' is a region on the continent of [[Essos]], located to the east of [[Westeros]] beyond the [[Narrow Sea]]. The Flatlands is a fertile area of open fields and plains, located around the [[Free Cities|Free City]] of [[Pentos]] and responsible for feeding it. Many [[Magister|magisters]] and nobles of the cities have estates on the Flatlands.&lt;ref&gt;[http://viewers-guide.hbo.com/game-of-thrones/season1/#!/locations/braavos/ HBO viewers guide, season 1 map, Braavos entry]&lt;/ref&gt;
